==Finnish==
===Etymology===
Yiddish, or more likely either Swedish or Russian origin.

===Noun===
'''kaveri'''

#[[pal]], [[friend]], [[buddy]], [[mate]]
#*Mene leikkimään kavereittesi kanssa!
#**Go to play with your pals!
#[[dude]], [[bloke]]
#*Kukas tuo kaveri on?
#**Who's that dude?

